## 3. RAG PIPELINE

Kompletni architektura RAG systemu nad judikaturou Ustavniho soudu.

### 3.1 Prehled vrstev (shora dolu)

```
User query
    ‚îÇ
    ‚ñº
[KROK 19] QueryRewriteService    ‚Äî LLM rewrite na presnejsi pravni dotaz (optional)
    ‚îÇ
    ‚ñº
[KROK 20] PlannerService         ‚Äî rozklad na 2-5 sub-queries (optional)
    ‚îÇ
    ‚ñº
[KROK 21] ExecutionService       ‚Äî spusti retrieval pro kazdy krok planu
    ‚îÇ         ‚îå‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îê
    ‚îÇ         ‚îÇ                              ‚îÇ
    ‚ñº         ‚ñº                              ‚ñº
[KROK 9]  DenseRetriever      [KROK 5]  KeywordRetriever
          (Qdrant + embedder)            (in-memory, BM25-like)
    ‚îÇ         ‚îÇ                              ‚îÇ
    ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î¨‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îò                              ‚îÇ
         ‚ñº                                   ‚îÇ
[KROK 5] fuse_results          ‚Üê‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îò
    ‚îÇ
    ‚ñº
[KROK 10/11] Reranker          ‚Äî SimpleReranker nebo CrossEncoderReranker (optional)
    ‚îÇ
    ‚ñº
[KROK 22] SynthesisService     ‚Äî LLM synteza odpovedi z ExecutionResult
    ‚îÇ
    ‚ñº
[KROK 24] OrchestratorService  ‚Äî konec-konec orchestrace: rewrite‚Üíplan‚Üíexecute‚Üísynthesize
    ‚îÇ
    ‚ñº
[KROK 25] FastAPI /query       ‚Äî POST /api/rag/query ‚Üí QueryResponse
```

### 3.2 KROK 1 ‚Äî Core: Logging a Tracing

**app/core/logging.py**

- `get_logger(name)` ‚Äî vraci nakonfigurovany logger
- respektuje `LOG_LEVEL` a `LOG_FILE` env promenne
- guard: `type(h) is logging.StreamHandler` (ne isinstance, protoze FileHandler dedi)
- modul-level flag `_configured` brani duplicate handlerum

**app/core/tracing.py**

- `trace_event(logger, name, **payload)` ‚Äî logi na DEBUG: `TRACE event.name | key=value`
- fallback na `str(value)` pro neserializovatelne typy (ne repr)

