```

**app/rag/retrieval/base.py** ‚Äî `BaseRetriever(ABC)` s `retrieve(query, top_k)`

**app/rag/retrieval/keyword_retriever.py** ‚Äî in-memory, score = min(0.3 + 0.1 * match_count, 0.9)

**app/rag/retrieval/fusion.py** ‚Äî dedup po id (zachova vyssi score), sort desc, top_k

