        # 4. llm.generate_text(prompt)
        # 5. fallback na "" kdyz LLM selze
```

Prompt architektura:

```
SYSTEM: You are a legal assistant specialized in constitutional law of the Czech Republic.
        Use only the provided case excerpts to answer. Do not hallucinate.
        If the excerpts do not contain sufficient information, say so explicitly.

USER:
User question:
{query}

Relevant case excerpts:
[chunk_id] (sk√≥re: 0.900)
{chunk text}
---
...

Instructions:
- Answer only from the provided excerpts
- Provide a structured legal explanation in Czech
- Cite specific decisions by their ID (e.g. III.√öS 255/22)
- Structure: Shrnut√≠ / Kl√≠ƒçov√© z√°vƒõry / Relevantn√≠ rozhodnut√≠
```

Vystup LLM je strukturovany cesky pravni text ‚Äî napr.:

```
## Shrnut√≠
...

## Kl√≠ƒçov√© z√°vƒõry
√östavn√≠ soud opakovanƒõ zd≈Øraznil...

## Relevantn√≠ rozhodnut√≠
III.√öS 255/22, III.√öS 401/22, II.√öS 100/21...
```

### 3.24 KROK 23 ‚Äî LLM Provider Adapters

Modularna vrstva HTTP provideru. Kazdy provider implementuje `BaseLLM` (structured output)
i `BaseTextLLM` (text-in/text-out).

**app/rag/llm/providers/_base.py** ‚Äî sdilena HTTP infrastruktura

