        # raise httpx.HTTPStatusError pri 4xx/5xx po vsech retry

def build_rag_messages(query, chunks) -> list[dict]:   # pro BaseLLM
def build_text_messages(prompt) -> list[dict]:          # pro BaseTextLLM
def to_claude_payload(messages) -> dict:                # konverze na Anthropic format
def parse_rag_response(body) -> LLMOutput:              # parsuje OpenAI-style response
def empty_output() -> LLMOutput:                        # fallback
```

Prompt injection ochrana: `_escape()` nahradi `{`/`}` za `(`/`)` v user inputu.

